            <title>联想 Y910 磁吸移动固态硬盘首销：2000MB/s 传输、重约 45g，1TB 售 559 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/821/944.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/821/944.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 14:36:27 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 1 月 2 日消息，联想 Y910 磁吸移动固态硬盘（PSSD）今日正式开售，新品宣称支持 2000MB/s 传输、重约 45g，售价 559 元起。</p><ul class="medium-size list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="text-align: left;">1TB：<strong>559&nbsp;元</strong></p></li><li><p style="text-align: left;">2TB：<strong>899&nbsp;元</strong></p></li></ul><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1410" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/12/e4b6bc5d-f43a-4866-8a40-6a01d03aa399.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExMy5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_11,x_11,a_0/format,f_auto" title="联想 Y910 磁吸移动固态硬盘首销：2000MB/s 传输、重约 45g，1TB 售 559 元" width="734" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/bOfg0p8" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/225498/5/16701/129795/67595459Fca78b4bd/17ddf5819aa731a8.jpg" title="联想 Y910 磁吸移动固态硬盘首销：2000MB/s 传输、重约 45g，1TB 售 559 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">联想（Lenovo）Y910 磁吸移动固态硬盘</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 559 元起</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1346" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/12/fbfef0a3-c529-4998-ad66-7b274cb3bb49.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEwNS5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_10,x_10,a_0/format,f_auto" title="联想 Y910 磁吸移动固态硬盘首销：2000MB/s 传输、重约 45g，1TB 售 559 元" width="682" /></p><p style="text-align: left;">联想 Y910 磁吸移动固态硬盘使用圆形外观 + 锌合金外壳 + 哑光黑配色设计，重约 45g，内置磁吸功能。硬盘配备配 USB-C 3.2 Gen2*2&nbsp;接口，支持&nbsp;<strong>1800-2000 MB/s 读速</strong>、<strong>1700-1900MB/s 写速</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1102" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/12/a174fb68-ffe7-4d38-a908-0